author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how Tariffs have been affecting all of our favourite games and systems and pretty much every electronic. A lot is being said right now so I wanted to cut through the noise and talk a bit about the future of not just gaming but most of the things we purchase. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Video Game Tariffs Are Insane...
